    "\n",
    "## Example 6 — Polynomial Forcing\n",
    "\n",
    "Solve $x'' + x' - 2x = t^2$.\n",
    "\n",
    ". . .\n",
    "\n",
    "**Eigenvalues:** $\\lambda^2+\\lambda-2=(\\lambda-1)(\\lambda+2)=0 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; \\lambda=1,-2$.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Homogeneous solution:** $x_h = C_1e^t + C_2e^{-2t}$.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Guess:** $x_p = At^2 + Bt + C$.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Substitute and match coefficients:**\n",
    "$$-2At^2 + (2A-2B)t + (2A+B-2C) = t^2$$\n",
