    "$$-2A=1 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; A=-\\tfrac{1}{2}, \\quad 2A-2B=0 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; B=-\\tfrac{1}{2}, \\quad 2A+B-2C=0 \\;\\Rightarrow\\; C=-\\tfrac{3}{4}$$\n",
